column2: BLACKOPS ONBOARD. NOW GO GO GO!
PAPA BEAR TO SAR PACKAGE. MISSION ABORTED WE LOST CONTACT TO THE ALPHA BLACK. RETURN TO BASE. OVER.

PAPA BEAR TO ALL FORCES. BLACK OPS SAFELY AT HOME BASE. MISSION ACCOMPLISHED. OVER.
